VALDEZ (SHIP); FISHING INDUSTRY -- ALASKA; ALEUTS; ANIMAL DEATHS; LIFESTYLES; 
VALDEZ (AK); HUNTING; PROPERTY DAMAGE; ENVIRONMENT 
</P>
