ACTIVISM; AUTOMOBILE INSURANCE; PROPOSITION 103 (STATE INSURANCE COMMISSIONER); 
LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; GILLESPIE, ROXANI M; COLLIS, CONWAY H; ROBBINS, 
ALAN; HAYDEN, TOM; NADER, RALPH; ROSENFIELD, HARVEY 
