USSR; BUSH, GEORGE; GERASIMOV, GENNADY I; ENGLAND -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; 
DEMONSTRATIONS -- ENGLAND; JEWS -- USSR; MILITARY FORCE REDUCTIONS; ARMS 
