-- LOS ANGELES; EARTHQUAKE SAFETY; FIRE SAFETY; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT 
BUILDINGS; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES -- WAGES AND SALARIES; LOS 
ANGELES -- FINANCES; POLICE STATIONS 
