<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Beckman Instruments Inc., Fullerton, has appointed Dennis Wilson to the newly 
established position of vice president, financial services. He will be 
responsible for the company's treasury, tax and insurance management. 
Previously, Wilson was vice president of corporate accounting and assistant 
controller with SmithKline Beckman in Philadelphia. In addition, the company 
also named Jay Steffenhagen manager of investor relations, responsible for all 
interaction between investors and Beckman Instruments. Steffenhagen has been 
with Beckman since 1979, serving most recently as strategic market manager. 
</P>
</TEXT>
